--------------------------------------------------------------------------
Bundled data (not covered by the Apache License)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------

Sources/SelfVerify/TrustAnchors/ contains the JPKI signing CA (公的個人認証
サービス 署名用CA) root certificates published by the Japan Agency for
Local Authority Information Systems (J-LIS, 地方公共団体情報システム機構).
These certificates are third-party public-key material, redistributed
unmodified for offline trust classification, and are not original works of
this project. Their SHA-256 fingerprints are recorded in
Sources/SelfVerify/JPKITrustAnchors.swift and shown in the app's About
screen, and were verified against the values published by J-LIS.
